subpages.markdown:
A page of results give you helpful information about navigating the other result pages.

Result pages look like this:

```json
{
  "content": [
	... the result page data ...
  ],
  "numberOfElements": 123,
  "firstPage": true,
  "lastPage": false,
  "totalPages": 7,
  "links": [
    {
      "rel": "first",
      "href": "http:/\ausdx.tk/api/search?query=car&page=1&size=20"
    },
    {
      "rel": "last",
      "href": "http:/ausdx.tk/api/search?query=car&page=7&size=20"
    },
    {
      "rel": "self",
      "href": "http://ausdx.tk/api/search?query=car&page=1&size=20"
    },
    {
      "rel": "next",
      "href": "http//:ausdx.tk/api/search?query=car&page=2&size=20"
    }
  ],
  "id": {
    "rel": "self",
    "href": "http://ausdx.tk/api/search?query=car&page=1&size=20"
  }
}
```
